From: Thiago Ribeiro <tmr.flu123123@hotmail.com>
Date: Thu, 16 Apr 2026 19:22:38 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] feat: debug logging (caixa-preta) + fix Date serialization +
 dedup

- Add debug_logs system: every message logs intent, handler, parsed data, response, errors, timing
- Add /debug page: dark mode dashboard showing last 50 logs with auto-refresh
- Add /api/debug endpoint serving log data
- Fix pending handler: hydrateParsed() reconstructs Date after JSON deserialization (root cause of 'Erro ao processar')
- Fix anomaly.ts: require min 5 transactions + 2.5x threshold (fixes false 'acima da media')
- Fix anomaly.ts: file was truncated, fully reconstructed
- Add message deduplication in webhook (3s window)
- Move pending check to Priority 2 in router (only undo overrides)
- Increase pending timeout to 10 minutes
- Add sql/create_debug_logs.sql migration
- Add tests/regression.md with 6 mandatory test cases
- Update painel.html with realistic percentages (60%)
